      <link>https://apnews.com/article/arson-wildlife-preserve-arizona-california-9ede0c1804221b45f865e2c688bd6a66</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当局表示，一名尤马男子因涉嫌在亚利桑那州西南部靠近加州边境的国家野生动物保护区引发野火而被捕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://apnews.com/article/arson-wildlife-preserve-arizona-california-9ede0c1804221b45f865e2c688bd6a66</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 16:45:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
